# TO INSTALL TFBOOST:

# Version of the installer when ROOT CERN is already installed
# and with a known path (es. /opt/root/6.xxx_install)
# also dependencies are checked, otherwise use script name 'packages'

0) FIRST COPY ALL THE SCRIPTS IN THE FOLDER WHERE YOU WANT TO INSTALL

1) OPEN A TERMINAL AND RUN:
   $ bash TFBoost_installer
   or
   $ bash TFBoost_installer_WSL
   if you are using Ubuntu with Windows Linux Subsystem
   

   
after TFBoost is configured and built, it can be runned 
with the GUI typing in a terminal: TFB
